R-Diff vendors source code from third-party projects in `targets/{authentic,synthetic}/*`.
The active samples and their upstream license identifiers are:

- `targets/authentic/php-8.1.0-dev`: PHP-3.01 (`https://opensource.org/license/php-3-01`)
- `targets/authentic/proftpd-1.3.3c`: GPL-2.0-or-later (`https://github.com/proftpd/proftpd/blob/master/COPYING`)
- `targets/authentic/vsftpd-2.3.4`: GPL-2.0-only (`https://github.com/dagwieers/vsftpd/blob/master/COPYING`)
- `targets/synthetic/dropbear2024-86`: MIT-style Dropbear license (`https://github.com/mkj/dropbear/blob/master/LICENSE`)
- `targets/synthetic/libpng-1.6.43`: libpng-2.0 (`https://github.com/pnggroup/libpng/blob/libpng16/LICENSE`)
- `targets/synthetic/libsndfile-1.2.2`: LGPL-2.1-or-later (`https://github.com/libsndfile/libsndfile/blob/master/COPYING`)
- `targets/synthetic/libtiff-4.3.0`: libtiff BSD-style license (`https://gitlab.com/libtiff/libtiff/-/blob/master/COPYRIGHT`)
- `targets/synthetic/libxml2-2.9.12`: MIT (`https://gitlab.gnome.org/GNOME/libxml2/-/blob/master/Copyright`)
- `targets/synthetic/lua-5.4.7`: MIT (`https://github.com/lua/lua/blob/master/README`)
- `targets/synthetic/openssl-3.0.0`: Apache-2.0 (`https://github.com/openssl/openssl/blob/master/LICENSE.txt`)
- `targets/synthetic/php-8.0.20`: PHP-3.01 (`https://opensource.org/license/php-3-01`)
- `targets/synthetic/poppler-21.07.0`: GPL-2.0-or-later (`https://gitlab.freedesktop.org/poppler/poppler/-/blob/master/COPYING`)
- `targets/synthetic/sqlite3-3.37.0`: Public Domain (`https://github.com/sqlite/sqlite/blob/master/LICENSE.md`)
- `targets/synthetic/sudo-1.9.15p5`: ISC-style sudo license (`https://www.sudo.ws/about/license/`)

R-Diff glue scripts, build logic, and documentation are provided under this
repository's own licensing terms. The upstream licenses above apply to the
vendored third-party source trees.
